data.title: Any Eagles Fans Out There? [Archive]
data.meta_description:
I've been a fan of the Eagles since they became popular in the 70s.  Of course, as most folks probably do, I get 'band burn out' from time-to-time, but have recently started listening to them again. 
 
On a recent trip, I listened to some of their songs on my iPOD and counted no less than 4 tunes that had mandolin bits in them.  The songs I found are: 
 
Saturday Night - Desperado Album (mando featured prominently) 
Hollywood Waltz - One Of These Nights 
I Love To Watch A Woman Dance - Long
